    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it must've been the very end of April.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And by the time we got to Majdanek, it may have been the beginning of-- of May.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in fact, people were coming-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with-- you know, other transports with people with terrible burns, people who jumped out the windows in the Warsaw Ghetto to escape the burning, you know, the-- the fires.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Are we still on?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
